    * Exit status (0 on normal exit, 1 on crash)


    * [Edit](https://github.sc-corp.net/Snapchat/studio3d-documentation/edit/main/api_generation/./api_editor/input/api_text_descriptions/LensStudio:Subprocess.Subprocess/properties/LensStudio:Subprocess.Subprocess-onExit.md)

